{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_01_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡って",
      "startTime": 0.13333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月スト、サニピ同時デビュー直後",
      "startTime": 1.6333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺達は、海沿いのキャンプ場に来ていた）\n（星見市のタウン誌でレジャースポットを紹介する仕事だ）",
      "startTime": 9.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（キャンプのことを綴った遙子さんのブログが）\n（編集者の目に留まり、記事のモデルに指名されたのだ）",
      "startTime": 15.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}君\nこっちのお肉、もういい感じだよ？",
      "startTime": 21.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あとこっちのタマネギも\nお野菜もちゃんと食べなきゃダメだよ？",
      "startTime": 27.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、子供じゃないんですから……\nそれにしても、遙子さん、やけに楽しそうですね",
      "startTime": 32.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうだね\nこういうの、久しぶりだからかなぁ",
      "startTime": 38.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "近場で日帰りとはいえ、キャンプしてるって思ったら\nなんだか楽しくなっちゃって……",
      "startTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "けど……意外でしたね\n遙子さんに一人キャンプの心得があったなんて",
      "startTime": 49.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "一人キャンプじゃなくって\n最近はソロキャンって言うのよ。覚えておいてね",
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの活動が始まる前は\nオフにちょこちょこソロキャンしてたのよ",
      "startTime": 61.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "最初はなんとな～く、自然の中に帰りたーい！\nって気持ちだけだったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 68.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "気付いたら楽しくなっちゃって\nあちこち出かけてみたの",
      "startTime": 73.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　ボーッとしてると\nマシュマロがドロドロになっちゃうよ？",
      "startTime": 77.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ていうか燃えちゃうから気を付けて\nそろそろ食べ頃だと思う",
      "startTime": 82.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "……んふふ～、これこれ～っ\nこのトロッとした甘さが病みつきなのよ～！",
      "startTime": 89.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "これも、キャンプ歴一年の知恵よ知恵",
      "startTime": 93.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。確かに今日の撮影も順調でしたし\n先方も遙子さんに頼んで正解だったって喜んでましたよ",
      "startTime": 100.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　それなら良かった……\nっていうか、安心した",
      "startTime": 107.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "安心ですか？",
      "startTime": 110.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "うん……自分の趣味が活かせたんだなって思うと\n凄くホッとしたの",
      "startTime": 116.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私ってその……地味、でしょ？\n趣味がパズルとか、いろいろ……",
      "startTime": 123.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "だけど一つぐらいは、こうして活かせるものが\nあったんだなって思って……",
      "startTime": 130.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるんですか……サニピのお姉さん役として\nみんなを支えてくれている……欠かせない存在です",
      "startTime": 136.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと……その言い方だと\n私が歳だって聞こえるんだけど……？",
      "startTime": 143.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "…………ふふっ、分かってる、冗談よ\n素直に受け止めておくね",
      "startTime": 149.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう",
      "startTime": 152.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_night",
      "startTime": 154.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ見て\n星、すごいよ",
      "startTime": 157.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……本当ですね\n東京じゃ、こんなには見えませんよね",
      "startTime": 163.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "うん……でも、より明るい星だけは\nどこでも輝いて見える……まるでアイドルみたい",
      "startTime": 169.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "一等星でしたっけ\n確かに、一握りだけの厳しい世界ですね",
      "startTime": 178.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "うん……星も、アイドルも\n一握りしか輝き続けることはできない",
      "startTime": 185.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、不思議なんだけど……\nさっき褒められたから、かな？",
      "startTime": 191.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "今なら私……もっと輝けるって思う",
      "startTime": 193.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "この星空みたいに沢山のアイドルがいる中で\nその一握りの一等星に……なれるかもしれない、って",
      "startTime": 201.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……なれますよ\nなっていきましょう……なさせてみせます",
      "startTime": 209.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "うん……でも、ふふっ……\nなさせてみせる、って、ちょっと日本語変じゃない？",
      "startTime": 216.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "もう……本当に大丈夫かなぁ？",
      "startTime": 220.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
